 "<p>Enter the text for the dropdown activity in to the dropdown field \nby either pasting text from another source or by typing text directly into the \nfield.<\/p><p> To select words to choose, double click on the word to select it and \nclick on the 'Hide\/Show' button below.<\/p>": "<p>Introdu\u00efu el text per a l'activitat de  men\u00fa desplegable en el camp \nde men\u00fa desplegable apegant el text des d'una altra font o teclejant el text directament al \ncamp.<\/p><p> Per a seleccionar paraules i amagar-les, feu doble clic en la paraula \nper a seleccionar-la i premeu \nel bot\u00f3 Oculta\/Mostra paraules.<\/p>", 
