 "Unlike the MCQ the SCORM quiz is used to test \nthe learners knowledge on a topic without providing the learner with feedback \nto the correct answer. The quiz will often be given once the learner has had \ntime to learn and practice using the information or skill.\n ": "A difer\u00e8ncia del q\u00fcestionari d'elecci\u00f3 m\u00faltiple (MCQ), el q\u00fcestionari SCORM \ns'utilitza per a avaluar els coneixements de l'alumnat sobre un tema sense donar cap \nretroacci\u00f3 a la resposta correcta. El q\u00fcestionari SCORM \nse sol passar quan l'alumnat ja ha tingut temps d'aprendre i practicar utilitzant la informaci\u00f3 o destresa.\n ", 
