 "Reflection is a teaching method often used to \nconnect theory to practice. Reflection tasks often provide learners with an \nopportunity to observe and reflect on their observations before presenting \nthese as a piece of academic work. Journals, diaries, profiles and portfolios \nare useful tools for collecting observation data. Rubrics and guides can be \neffective feedback tools.": "La reflexi\u00f3 \u00e9s un m\u00e8tode que s'utilitza sovint per a\nconnectar teoria i pr\u00e0ctica. Les tasques de reflexi\u00f3 proporcionen a l'alumnat \nl'oportunitat d'observar i reflexionar sobre les observacions pr\u00f2pies abans de presentar-les \ncom a part del treball acad\u00e8mic. Peri\u00f2dics, revistes, \nrevistes, perfils i dossiers \ns\u00f3n recursos \u00fatils per a arreplegar dades de l'observaci\u00f3. Els comentaris i les orientacions \ns\u00f3n recursos efectius per a la retroacci\u00f3.", 
